},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T15:02:12.000Z","msg":"咁又係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每個月都儲到約10k<br />\n咁又未必冇錢 祇係覺得唔值得付出咁多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n買衫都係屋企人覺得要買先推我去買<br />\n根本冇興趣自己買衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5236f58d8fdf8116c1a6eab76b1ec6072bf54a03","tid":566011,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"027b673f02ab8ecf1a177ee8e6f0b1e7e95d8a29","tid":566011,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61d42336af65532c10e9a7b0b9e5c73311e1f295","tid":566011,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T14:38:24.000Z","msg":"溝下女 或者會多返啲樂趣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T14:58:10.000Z","msg":"down AV打丁已經好滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T15:05:11.000Z","msg":"再打丁你人生就繼續冇意義了"},{"pid":"cb6a33f9bc64938d10885a7c457d3654050f55e5","tid":566011,"uid":76114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T15:10:50.000Z","msg":"留名。<br />\n我都一樣，我比你好少少嘅就係對籃球嘅熱血。有時間就落會打波，冇人就單丁練波。<br />\n我覺得我就黎要同人講 我條女姓籃名球<br />\n份糧除左買籃球野 真係冇地方洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c792a88872b9d10f394825602d6c3c264692209","tid":566011,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5236f58d8fdf8116c1a6eab76b1ec6072bf54a03","tid":566011,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"027b673f02ab8ecf1a177ee8e6f0b1e7e95d8a29","tid":566011,"uid":49004,"lik